---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import SchemaOrg from '../../components/seo/SchemaOrg.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Material Exclusivo | Una Voz al paso del Eclipse — AdriCris Rueda"
  description="Descubre el material exclusivo de Una Voz al paso del Eclipse: la carta regalo de Natalia y la playlist oficial en Spotify."
  image="/images/portada-libro-2.png"
  keywords={['Una Voz al paso del Eclipse', 'material exclusivo', 'carta Natalia', 'playlist Spotify', 'AdriCris Rueda']}
>
  <SchemaOrg
    slot="head"
    type={['Book']}
    data={{
      name: 'Una Voz al paso del Eclipse',
      genre: 'Crecimiento Espiritual',
      description: 'Material exclusivo del libro: carta regalo de Natalia y playlist oficial en Spotify.',
      url: 'https://adricrisrueda.com/una-voz-al-paso-del-eclipse/material-exclusivo',
    }}
  />
  <SchemaOrg
    slot="head"
    type={['BreadcrumbList']}
    breadcrumbs={[
      { name: 'Inicio', url: '/' },
      { name: 'Biblioteca', url: '/libros' },
      { name: 'Una Voz al paso del Eclipse', url: '/libro' },
      { name: 'Material Exclusivo', url: '/una-voz-al-paso-del-eclipse/material-exclusivo' },
    ]}
  />

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <header class="relative min-h-[70vh] flex items-center justify-center pt-24 overflow-hidden bg-background-light dark:bg-background-dark">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden pointer-events-none">
      <div class="absolute top-[-10%] right-[-10%] w-[50%] h-[60%] bg-secondary/10 dark:bg-secondary/5 blur-[100px] rounded-full"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-[-10%] left-[-10%] w-[45%] h-[55%] bg-accent/10 dark:bg-accent/5 blur-[100px] rounded-full"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10 w-full text-center">
      <span class="text-secondary tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-xs font-semibold block mb-6">Material Exclusivo</span>
      <h1 class="font-display text-5xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl leading-tight text-primary dark:text-white mb-8">
        Nos vemos al<br/>
        <span class="italic text-accent font-light">otro lado del eclipse</span>
      </h1>
      <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-secondary mx-auto rounded-full mb-10"></div>
      <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto space-y-6 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 font-light text-lg leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          De una u otra forma, ya eres parte de mi vida. A través de estas páginas abrí mi corazón y compartí contigo lo que he podido observar durante estos cincuenta años —sí, los mismos de Natalia— en las historias de personas que conozco y en las de quienes no, pero que, como tú y como yo, viven, ríen y lloran.
        </p>
        <p>
          Sin embargo, algunas historias no terminan cuando se cierra un libro. Hay momentos que quedaron fuera de estas páginas. Instantes que también merecen ser contados.
        </p>
        <p class="text-primary dark:text-accent font-medium italic">
          Así como en el cumpleaños de Natalia hubo regalos para ella, también quiso dejarte uno a ti.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-8 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2">
      <a class="animate-bounce p-2 text-primary dark:text-accent/70 hover:text-secondary transition-colors" href="#material">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl">keyboard_arrow_down</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- Material Exclusivo Section -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-white dark:bg-surface-dark relative" id="material">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <span class="text-secondary font-bold tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-xs block mb-4">Para ti, lector</span>
        <h2 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl text-primary dark:text-white mb-4">Descúbrelo</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-500 font-light max-w-xl mx-auto">
          Estos son los regalos que Natalia quiso dejarte. Momentos que merecen ser vividos más allá de las páginas.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-10">
        <!-- Carta de Natalia -->
        <div class="group bg-background-light dark:bg-background-dark rounded-[2rem] p-10 hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 relative overflow-hidden border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-800 flex flex-col">
          <div class="absolute -right-10 -top-10 w-40 h-40 bg-secondary/10 rounded-full blur-2xl group-hover:bg-secondary/20 transition-colors"></div>
          <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col h-full">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-white dark:bg-surface-dark shadow-sm flex items-center justify-center mb-8 text-secondary group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl">mail</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-2xl text-primary dark:text-white mb-3">Carta regalo de Natalia</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 font-light leading-relaxed mb-8 flex-grow">
              Una carta escrita desde el corazón de Natalia para ti. Palabras que no encontraron espacio en el libro pero que guardan la esencia de su viaje.
            </p>
            <a
              href="/downloads/carta-regalo-natalia.pdf"
              download
              class="gold-gradient hover:opacity-90 text-primary px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-display font-bold tracking-wide transition-all shadow-lg shadow-secondary/30 hover:shadow-secondary/50 transform hover:-translate-y-1 inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 w-full"
            >
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined">download</span>
              DESCARGAR CARTA
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Playlist Spotify -->
        <div class="group bg-background-light dark:bg-background-dark rounded-[2rem] p-10 hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 relative overflow-hidden border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-800 flex flex-col">
          <div class="absolute -right-10 -top-10 w-40 h-40 bg-[#1DB954]/10 rounded-full blur-2xl group-hover:bg-[#1DB954]/20 transition-colors"></div>
          <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col h-full">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-white dark:bg-surface-dark shadow-sm flex items-center justify-center mb-8 text-[#1DB954] group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                <path d="M12 0C5.4 0 0 5.4 0 12s5.4 12 12 12 12-5.4 12-12S18.66 0 12 0zm5.521 17.34c-.24.359-.66.48-1.021.24-2.82-1.74-6.36-2.101-10.561-1.141-.418.122-.779-.179-.899-.539-.12-.421.18-.78.54-.9 4.56-1.021 8.52-.6 11.64 1.32.42.18.479.659.301 1.02zm1.44-3.3c-.301.42-.841.6-1.262.3-3.239-1.98-8.159-2.58-11.939-1.38-.479.12-1.02-.12-1.14-.6-.12-.48.12-1.021.6-1.141C9.6 9.9 15 10.561 18.72 12.84c.361.181.54.78.241 1.2zm.12-3.36C15.24 8.4 8.82 8.16 5.16 9.301c-.6.179-1.2-.181-1.38-.721-.18-.601.18-1.2.72-1.381 4.26-1.26 11.28-1.02 15.721 1.621.539.3.719 1.02.419 1.56-.299.421-1.02.599-1.559.3z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-2xl text-primary dark:text-white mb-3">Playlist Oficial</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 font-light leading-relaxed mb-8 flex-grow italic">
              "Algunas fotografías guardan historias en silencio.<br/>Algunas canciones también.<br/>Escucha aquí la playlist oficial de Una voz al paso del eclipse."
            </p>
            <a
              href="https://open.spotify.com/playlist/69hw6Gi3b8Pu4B6ye5w9QE?si=bgJqVaT3Qymo2ed3R8P3FQ"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="bg-[#1DB954] hover:bg-[#1ed760] text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-display font-bold tracking-wide transition-all shadow-lg shadow-[#1DB954]/30 hover:shadow-[#1DB954]/50 transform hover:-translate-y-1 inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 w-full"
            >
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                <path d="M12 0C5.4 0 0 5.4 0 12s5.4 12 12 12 12-5.4 12-12S18.66 0 12 0zm5.521 17.34c-.24.359-.66.48-1.021.24-2.82-1.74-6.36-2.101-10.561-1.141-.418.122-.779-.179-.899-.539-.12-.421.18-.78.54-.9 4.56-1.021 8.52-.6 11.64 1.32.42.18.479.659.301 1.02zm1.44-3.3c-.301.42-.841.6-1.262.3-3.239-1.98-8.159-2.58-11.939-1.38-.479.12-1.02-.12-1.14-.6-.12-.48.12-1.021.6-1.141C9.6 9.9 15 10.561 18.72 12.84c.361.181.54.78.241 1.2zm.12-3.36C15.24 8.4 8.82 8.16 5.16 9.301c-.6.179-1.2-.181-1.38-.721-.18-.601.18-1.2.72-1.381 4.26-1.26 11.28-1.02 15.721 1.621.539.3.719 1.02.419 1.56-.299.421-1.02.599-1.559.3z"/>
              </svg>
              ESCUCHAR EN SPOTIFY
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Conexión Section -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-primary dark:bg-background-dark relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
      <svg class="w-full h-full" preserveAspectRatio="none" viewBox="0 0 100 100">
        <path d="M0 100 C 30 50 70 80 100 30 L 100 100 Z" fill="#E3B64C"></path>
      </svg>
    </div>
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-5xl text-secondary mb-6 block">favorite</span>
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl text-white mb-6">Gracias por acompañar a Natalia hasta el final</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-200 font-light text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Esta historia es solo una puerta. Si lo que leíste resuena en ti, hay muchos más caminos por recorrer juntos.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
        <!-- Servicios -->
        <a href="/servicios" class="group bg-white/5 hover:bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-secondary/20 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-5 group-hover:bg-secondary/30 transition-colors">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl text-secondary">spa</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-xl text-white mb-3">Terapias & Talleres</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300 font-light text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Sesiones individuales y experiencias grupales para seguir tu propio camino de sanación.
          </p>
        </a>

        <!-- Más libros -->
        <a href="/libros" class="group bg-white/5 hover:bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-secondary/20 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-5 group-hover:bg-secondary/30 transition-colors">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl text-secondary">auto_stories</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-xl text-white mb-3">Más historias</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300 font-light text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Descubre el resto de la biblioteca de AdriCris. Cada libro es un viaje diferente hacia ti mismo.
          </p>
        </a>

        <!-- Conectar -->
        <a href="https://wa.me/573132979675?text=Hola%20Adri!%20Terminé%20de%20leer%20Una%20Voz%20al%20paso%20del%20Eclipse%20y%20me%20gustaría%20conectar%20contigo%20:)%20" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="group bg-white/5 hover:bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-secondary/20 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-5 group-hover:bg-secondary/30 transition-colors">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl text-secondary">chat</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-xl text-white mb-3">Escríbele a Adri</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300 font-light text-sm leading-relaxed">
            ¿Te gustaría compartir lo que sentiste al leer? Adriana lee y responde cada mensaje personalmente.
          </p>
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Redes sociales -->
      <div class="text-center border-t border-white/10 pt-12">
        <p class="text-gray-300 font-light mb-6">Sigue el día a día de AdriCris en sus redes</p>
        <div class="flex justify-center gap-4">
          <a href="https://www.facebook.com/adricrisrueda/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-white/10 hover:bg-secondary/20 border border-white/10 flex items-center justify-center text-white hover:text-secondary transition-all" aria-label="Facebook">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M22 12c0-5.523-4.477-10-10-10S2 6.477 2 12c0 4.991 3.657 9.128 8.438 9.878v-6.987h-2.54V12h2.54V9.797c0-2.506 1.492-3.89 3.777-3.89 1.094 0 2.238.195 2.238.195v2.46h-1.26c-1.243 0-1.63.771-1.63 1.562V12h2.773l-.443 2.89h-2.33v6.988C18.343 21.128 22 16.991 22 12z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a href="https://www.instagram.com/adricrisrueda/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-white/10 hover:bg-secondary/20 border border-white/10 flex items-center justify-center text-white hover:text-secondary transition-all" aria-label="Instagram">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M12.315 2c2.43 0 2.784.013 3.808.06 1.064.049 1.791.218 2.427.465a4.902 4.902 0 011.772 1.153 4.902 4.902 0 011.153 1.772c.247.636.416 1.363.465 2.427.048 1.067.06 1.407.06 4.123v.08c0 2.643-.012 2.987-.06 4.043-.049 1.064-.218 1.791-.465 2.427a4.902 4.902 0 01-1.153 1.772 4.902 4.902 0 01-1.772 1.153c-.636.247-1.363.416-2.427.465-1.067.048-1.407.06-4.123.06h-.08c-2.643 0-2.987-.012-4.043-.06-1.064-.049-1.791-.218-2.427-.465a4.902 4.902 0 01-1.772-1.153 4.902 4.902 0 01-1.153-1.772c-.247-.636-.416-1.363-.465-2.427-.047-1.024-.06-1.379-.06-3.808v-.63c0-2.43.013-2.784.06-3.808.049-1.064.218-1.791.465-2.427a4.902 4.902 0 011.153-1.772A4.902 4.902 0 015.468 2.53c.636-.247 1.363-.416 2.427-.465C8.901 2.013 9.256 2 11.685 2h.63zm-.081 1.802h-.468c-2.456 0-2.784.011-3.807.058-.975.045-1.504.207-1.857.344-.467.182-.8.398-1.15.748-.35.35-.566.683-.748 1.15-.137.353-.3.882-.344 1.857-.047 1.023-.058 1.351-.058 3.807v.468c0 2.456.011 2.784.058 3.807.045.975.207 1.504.344 1.857.182.466.399.8.748 1.15.35.35.683.566 1.15.748.353.137.882.3 1.857.344 1.054.048 1.37.058 4.041.058h.08c2.597 0 2.917-.01 3.96-.058.976-.045 1.505-.207 1.858-.344.466-.182.8-.398 1.15-.748.35-.35.566-.683.748-1.15.137-.353.3-.882.344-1.857.048-1.055.058-1.37.058-4.041v-.08c0-2.597-.01-2.917-.058-3.96-.045-.976-.207-1.505-.344-1.858a3.097 3.097 0 00-.748-1.15 3.098 3.098 0 00-1.15-.748c-.353-.137-.882-.3-1.857-.344-1.023-.047-1.351-.058-3.807-.058zM12 6.865a5.135 5.135 0 110 10.27 5.135 5.135 0 010-10.27zm0 1.802a3.333 3.333 0 100 6.666 3.333 3.333 0 000-6.666zm5.338-3.205a1.2 1.2 0 110 2.4 1.2 1.2 0 010-2.4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@adricrisrueda" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-white/10 hover:bg-secondary/20 border border-white/10 flex items-center justify-center text-white hover:text-secondary transition-all" aria-label="YouTube">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M19.812 5.418c.861.23 1.538.907 1.768 1.768C21.998 8.746 22 12 22 12s0 3.255-.418 4.814a2.504 2.504 0 0 1-1.768 1.768c-1.56.419-7.814.419-7.814.419s-6.255 0-7.814-.419a2.505 2.505 0 0 1-1.768-1.768C2 15.255 2 12 2 12s0-3.255.417-4.814a2.507 2.507 0 0 1 1.768-1.768C5.744 5 11.998 5 11.998 5s6.255 0 7.814.418ZM15.194 12 10 15V9l5.194 3Z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a href="https://co.linkedin.com/in/adriana-cristina-rueda" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-white/10 hover:bg-secondary/20 border border-white/10 flex items-center justify-center text-white hover:text-secondary transition-all" aria-label="LinkedIn">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433a2.062 2.062 0 01-2.063-2.065 2.064 2.064 0 112.063 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer mini -->
  <section class="py-12 bg-surface-light dark:bg-surface-dark border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <p class="text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 font-light text-xs mb-6">
        Si deseas compartir una imagen del libro o un fragmento que te haya acompañado, puedes hacerlo con: <span class="text-secondary font-medium">#UnaVozAlPasoDelEclipse</span>
      </p>
      <div class="flex justify-center space-x-4 mb-6">
        <a href="https://www.facebook.com/adricrisrueda/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-white dark:bg-surface-dark border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 flex items-center justify-center text-gray-500 hover:text-secondary hover:border-secondary transition-all" aria-label="Facebook">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M22 12c0-5.523-4.477-10-10-10S2 6.477 2 12c0 4.991 3.657 9.128 8.438 9.878v-6.987h-2.54V12h2.54V9.797c0-2.506 1.492-3.89 3.777-3.89 1.094 0 2.238.195 2.238.195v2.46h-1.26c-1.243 0-1.63.771-1.63 1.562V12h2.773l-.443 2.89h-2.33v6.988C18.343 21.128 22 16.991 22 12z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
        </a>
